vernac_cmds: Inductive PULB_ob : Type := | P1 : PULB_ob | P2 : PULB_ob | P3 : PULB_ob.
Inductive PULB_mor : PULB_ob -> PULB_ob -> Type := | IP1 : PULB_mor P1 P1 | IP2 : PULB_mor P2 P2 | IP3 : PULB_mor P3 P3 | F12 : PULB_mor P1 P2 | F32 : PULB_mor P3 P2.
Lemma PULB_11_P : (PULB_mor P1 P1 -> Prop) -> forall a b : PULB_ob, PULB_mor a b -> Prop.
intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_11_ind : forall P : PULB_mor P1 P1 -> Prop, P IP1 -> forall x : PULB_mor P1 P1, P x.
apply (PULB_mor_ind (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_11_P P f)); simpl in |- *.
Lemma PULB_22_P : (PULB_mor P2 P2 -> Prop) -> forall a b : PULB_ob, PULB_mor a b -> Prop.
intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_22_ind : forall P : PULB_mor P2 P2 -> Prop, P IP2 -> forall x : PULB_mor P2 P2, P x.
apply (PULB_mor_ind (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_22_P P f)); simpl in |- *.

intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_33_ind : forall P : PULB_mor P3 P3 -> Prop, P IP3 -> forall x : PULB_mor P3 P3, P x.
apply (PULB_mor_ind (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_33_P P f)); simpl in |- *.
Lemma PULB_12_P : (PULB_mor P1 P2 -> Prop) -> forall a b : PULB_ob, PULB_mor a b -> Prop.
intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_12_ind : forall P : PULB_mor P1 P2 -> Prop, P F12 -> forall x : PULB_mor P1 P2, P x.

Lemma PULB_32_ind : forall P : PULB_mor P3 P2 -> Prop, P F32 -> forall x : PULB_mor P3 P2, P x.

Lemma PULB_21_P : (PULB_mor P2 P1 -> Prop) -> forall a b : PULB_ob, PULB_mor a b -> Prop.
intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_21_ind : forall (P : PULB_mor P2 P1 -> Prop) (x : PULB_mor P2 P1), P x.
apply (PULB_mor_ind (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_21_P P f)); simpl in |- *; auto.
Lemma PULB_21_T : (PULB_mor P2 P1 -> Type) -> forall a b : PULB_ob, PULB_mor a b -> Type.
intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_21_rect : forall (P : PULB_mor P2 P1 -> Type) (x : PULB_mor P2 P1), P x.
apply (PULB_mor_rect (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_21_T P f)); simpl in |- *; auto.

Lemma PULB_31_rect : forall (P : PULB_mor P3 P1 -> Type) (x : PULB_mor P3 P1), P x.

intros P a b; elim a; elim b.

apply (PULB_mor_ind (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_23_P P f)); simpl in |- *; auto.
Lemma PULB_23_T : (PULB_mor P2 P3 -> Type) -> forall a b : PULB_ob, PULB_mor a b -> Type.
intros P a b; elim a; elim b.
Lemma PULB_23_rect : forall (P : PULB_mor P2 P3 -> Type) (x : PULB_mor P2 P3), P x.
apply (PULB_mor_rect (P:=fun (a b : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor a b) => PULB_23_T P f)); simpl in |- *; auto.
Definition Equal_PULB_mor (f g : PULB_mor a b) := True.
apply Build_Equivalence; [ trivial | apply Build_Partial_equivalence ]; red in |- *; unfold Equal_PULB_mor in |- *; simpl in |- *; auto.

Definition Comp_PULB_mor (a b c : PULB_ob) (f : PULB_mor_setoid a b) := match f in (PULB_mor p p0) return (PULB_mor_setoid p0 c -> PULB_mor_setoid p c) with | IP1 => match c as p return (PULB_mor P1 p -> PULB_mor P1 p) with | P1 => fun _ => IP1 | P2 => fun _ => F12 | P3 => fun g => PULB_13_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P1 P3 => PULB_mor P1 P3) g end | IP2 => match c as p return (PULB_mor P2 p -> PULB_mor P2 p) with | P1 => fun g => PULB_21_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P2 P1 => PULB_mor P2 P1) g | P2 => fun _ => IP2 | P3 => fun g => PULB_23_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P2 P3 => PULB_mor P2 P3) g end | IP3 => match c as p return (PULB_mor P3 p -> PULB_mor P3 p) with | P1 => fun g => PULB_31_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P3 P1 => PULB_mor P3 P1) g | P2 => fun _ => F32 | P3 => fun _ => IP3 end | F12 => match c as p return (PULB_mor P2 p -> PULB_mor P1 p) with | P1 => fun g => PULB_21_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P2 P1 => PULB_mor P1 P1) g | P2 => fun _ => F12 | P3 => fun g => PULB_23_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P2 P3 => PULB_mor P1 P3) g end | F32 => match c as p return (PULB_mor P2 p -> PULB_mor P3 p) with | P1 => fun g => PULB_21_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P2 P1 => PULB_mor P3 P1) g | P2 => fun _ => F32 | P3 => fun g => PULB_23_rect (fun _ : PULB_mor P2 P3 => PULB_mor P3 P3) g end end.
unfold Congl_law, Equal_PULB_mor in |- *; simpl in |- *; auto.
unfold Congr_law, Equal_PULB_mor in |- *; simpl in |- *; auto.
unfold Assoc_law in |- *; simpl in |- *; unfold Equal_PULB_mor in |- *; simpl in |- *; auto.
Definition Id_PULB (a : PULB_ob) := match a as a' return (PULB_mor a' a') with | P1 => IP1 | P2 => IP2 | P3 => IP3 end.
unfold Idl_law in |- *; simpl in |- *; unfold Equal_PULB_mor in |- *; simpl in |- *; auto.
unfold Idr_law in |- *; simpl in |- *; unfold Equal_PULB_mor in |- *; simpl in |- *; auto.
Canonical Structure PULB := Build_Category Assoc_PULB Idl_PULB Idr_PULB.
